HEADWORD: Sargasso
<hw>Sar*gas"so</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.
<ets>sargazo</ets> seaweed.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The gulf weed.
See under <er>Gulf</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sargasso Sea</b></col>, <cd>a large tract of the North
Atlantic Ocean where sargasso in great abundance floats on the
surface.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

